. Julieta received 10% less money in tips than Rafaela. How much money did Julieta and Rafaela receive as tips altogether?\n\nReasoning:\n- Each of the forty customers who came into the restaurant gave Rafaela a $20 tip.\n- Julieta received 10% less money in tips than Rafaela.\n- As a result, Julieta received a total of $20 less in tips than Rafaela.\n- Therefore, the total amount of tips received by both Rafaela and Julieta is $180.': 1}
